-- BHP Billiton, Rio, Xstrata Agree to Key Elements on Mine Tax, Herald Says
-- Tim Smith
-- 2010-07-01T04:12:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/bhp-billiton-rio-xstrata-agree-to-key-elements-on-mine-tax-herald-says.html

          
          
             BHP Billiton Ltd., Rio Tinto Group
and Xstrata Plc have agreed with the Australian government on
key elements of a new resources tax structure, the Sydney
Morning Herald reported on its website, without saying where it
got the information.  
